{"id":"805921661393272833","type":"text","timestamp":1768586789,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/805921661393272833","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":true,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/faintv0x/792549185247494144\">faintv0x</a>:</p><blockquote><p>The creator of the lesbian flag, Emily Gwen, is currently unhoused and struggling financially while suffering to chronic and mental illness. </p><p>I have already contributed to her Kofi, and now I ask you to help, especially if you have ever used the lesbian flag. Even if you can&rsquo;t donate, I urge you to share her Kofi around to reach more audiences</p><p>Lesbians support other lesbians 🧡🤍💗</p><div class=\"npf_row\"><div><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"1492\" data-orig-width=\"1096\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/53aac59bae8a3b93e6f8eaa7adeadb9f/5be575111586b12c-9b/s640x960/2330c720d1039206cec97c57bc929e295cf4bf7d.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"1492\" data-orig-width=\"1096\" alt=\"I am so sorry I have to beg. Things are not good and I don't know how I'm going to be able to find a place to live and pay the deposit when I can't even afford the basic necessities to live. But even $1 helps. https://t.co/m2vAF8JbAy\n\n— Emily Gwen (@theemilygwen) August 19, 2025\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/53aac59bae8a3b93e6f8eaa7adeadb9f/5be575111586b12c-9b/s75x75_c1/e1057ac2570cd8922b082a4442245f037050749d.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/53aac59bae8a3b93e6f8eaa7adeadb9f/5be575111586b12c-9b/s100x200/eb843da62e1a93b4cb87d58a74bc6308c920ead2.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/53aac59bae8a3b93e6f8eaa7adeadb9f/5be575111586b12c-9b/s250x400/fe17d2dafab5dd5d8f908557be6af32382a5ab53.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/53aac59bae8a3b93e6f8eaa7adeadb9f/5be575111586b12c-9b/s400x600/b85eccea96c2d6516551d65a019c22f84503c1e0.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/53aac59bae8a3b93e6f8eaa7adeadb9f/5be575111586b12c